97
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:17,000
And me and Meyer--
we were both the leader.

98
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,000
At least it
started out that way.

99
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,000
Just four mugs
off the street.

100
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:24,000
