128
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:32,000
You just did it, kid.

129
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:39,000
Get lost.

130
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:42,000
Now do
you see?

131
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:46,000
Between you and me,
we're equals.

132
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:50,000
But other people,
