Who's this friend?

145
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:34,000
Arnold Rothstein.

146
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:39,000
No disrespect, Tommy.
Why would Rothstein wanna do
business with bums like us?

147
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:43,000
