when you go to his hotel.

149
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:54,000
No one ever
called you all bums.

150
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:57,000
Come on.

151
00:12:57,000 --> 00:13:01,000
It's very
good stuff.

152
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:03,000
Come on in, fellas.

153
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:07,000
