I don't have a wife.

167
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:52,000
- Why not?
- Emotion is dangerous.

168
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:56,000
- Aren't you human?
- Would it help?

169
00:13:56,000 --> 00:14:02,000
Next. I have ships
and distilleries in Scotland.

170
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:04,000
