this guy? I'm 24 years old--

182
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,000
Money!

183
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:53,000
Everything is
money, Charlie.

184
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:56,000
Don't ever forget it.

185
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:59,000
But you, you'll
never make any money.

186
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:15,000
