to burn, Charlie.

192
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:57,000
Wanna burn some?
Want to? Want to?

193
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:03,000
Be my guest.
All right!

194
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:05,000
Everybody ready?

195
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:08,000
The party.
Our first million.

196
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:11,000
Paisan, you ready
to make some money?
I'm ready.

197
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:14,000
- I'm always ready.
-Just don't hog all the broads.

198
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:16,000
I can't help it.
They're all over me.

199
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:20,000
Tell us something
we don't know, huh?
Gentlemen,

200
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:24,000
