01:24:45,000 --> 01:24:48,000
Huh?

1041
01:24:48,000 --> 01:24:52,000
I'm scared.

1042
01:24:52,000 --> 01:24:55,000
Everything I want...

1043
01:24:55,000 --> 01:26:05,000
