All I have to do is take it.

1044
01:26:05,000 --> 01:28:22,000
Morning.
Mmm.

1045
01:28:22,000 --> 01:28:53,000
Oh,Jesus Christ.

1046
01:28:53,000 --> 01:28:56,000
Name it, Frankie.
Anything.

1047
01:28:56,000 --> 01:28:59,000
Whatever the department
can do.

1048
01:28:59,000 --> 01:29:02,000
