1068
01:30:28,000 --> 01:30:33,000
When he walks in,
put him on ice.

1069
01:30:33,000 --> 01:30:41,000
My pleasure.

1070
01:30:41,000 --> 01:30:45,000
Here's my key. 31 2.

1071
01:30:45,000 --> 01:30:48,000
Yes, absolutely.

1072
01:30:48,000 --> 01:30:51,000
Mr. Coll, I sent
your room service.

1073
01:30:51,000 --> 01:30:53,000
It must be on its way.
I don't know.

1074
01:30:53,000 --> 01:30:56,000
You don't know if
it's on the way up?

1075
01:30:56,000 --> 01:30:59,000
I'm sorry, Mr. Coll.
Give it to me again.

1076
01:30:59,000 --> 01:31:02,000
I want two eggs up.
I want a rasher of bacon.

1077
01:31:02,000 --> 01:31:03,000
I want a pot of coffee, black.
