to hit you in case you knew.

1146
01:36:26,000 --> 01:36:28,000
And all of you shrug?

1147
01:36:28,000 --> 01:36:33,000
Except some of you
are friends ofJoe's.

1148
01:36:33,000 --> 01:36:37,000
