1156
01:37:05,000 --> 01:37:07,000
That's right.

1157
01:37:07,000 --> 01:37:11,000
Everybody here...
is equal.

1158
01:37:11,000 --> 01:37:16,000
Corporations have
a board of directors.

1159
01:37:16,000 --> 01:37:21,000
So will we.
